uint32_t sbllibAppImageParseParams::skipDDRCopy

Skip DDR copy. Set to 1 when AppImage is already DDR. One such case is EVELOADER on IPU in VisionSDK with A15-Linux. In this case only gMediaReadFxn is used by SBLLIB
